        <profileDesc>
            <creation/>
            <abstract>
                <p>This record refers to a collection of prayers and miracles of the Trinity attested in 
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ANLcr62"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">More than 1 ANLcr62</span></ref> arranged according to the days of the week. While
                    its structure, introduction and miracles are identical to <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2296Sayfas">Sayfa Śǝllāse</ref>, the content
                    of the prayers is different and instead largely corresponds to <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer">Prayer for the weekdays</ref>.</p>
            </abstract>
