        <body>
            <div type="bibliography">
                
            </div>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
                <note>The following division into textparts follows
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ANLcr62"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">More than 1 ANLcr62</span></ref>.</note>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Introduction" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7330IntroZenSe">
                    <label>Introduction</label>
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="incipit">
                        <ab>
                            በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩ አምላክ፡ ስቡሕ፡ ወእኩት፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ ዜና፡ ነገሮሙ፡ ጽሒፎቶሰ፡ ኢንክል፡ አላ፡ በከመ፡ አክሀለነ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ነጊረ፡ ውዳሴሆሙሰ፡
                            ኢይክሉ፡ ሰማይ፡ ወምድር፡ ክርታስ፨ ወኢየአክል፡ ማየ፡ ባሕር፡ ቀለመ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወመላእክት፡ ጸሐፍያነ፡ ወዓለምኖ፡ እሚያግመሮ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                            ወእንዘ፡ ሀለዉ፡ ቅድመ፡ እንበለ፡ ይፍጥሩ፡ ሰማየ፡ ወምድረ፡ ፫ አካላት፡ ወ፩ በመለኮት፡ ኅቡረ፡ በሥምረት፡ ወበሕይወት፡ በባሕርይ፡ ወበእዘዝ፡ እንዘ፡ ኢይትፈለጡ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="explicit">
                        <ab>
                            ወሶበ፡ ይቤልዎሙ፡ ዘንተ፡ አኃዙ፡ ይትዋለዱ፡ ወይቤሉ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እንዘ፡ ይትነበብ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ይጸልቡ፡ በላዕሌሁ፡ ቀጠንተ፡ አልባሰ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡ ያፅምዕዎ፡
                            እንዘ፡ ይትነበብ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ወዘኢያጸምዖ፡ ለውእቱ፡ ቃል፡ ይኩን፡ ውጉዘ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አንሰ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ አነ፡ ገብርክሙ፡
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="supplication">
                        <ab>
                            ወጸሐፌ፡ ዜናክሙ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሱ፡ ከመ፡ ታብኡኒ፡ ውስተ፡ ደብረ፡ ጽዮን፡ ምርፋቅ። ወከመ፡ ትባልሕዋ፡ ለነፍስየ፡ እምጋኔነ፡ ቀትር፡ ወድድቀ፡ ወታንብርዋ፡ ሊቃናት፡ በጽድቅ፡
                            ወትባርክዋ፡ ለመስቀል፡ ዘወርቅ፡ ወለኵልነ፡ ንበል፡ ኅቡረ፡ ይዕቀቡነ፡ በጽድቀ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Monday">
                    <label>Monday</label>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerAmlakiya" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Monday">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ሰኑይ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አምላኪየ፡ ዓቢይ፡ ወግሩም፡ ዘአልቦ፡ ጥንት፡ ወኢተፍጻሜት፡ 
                                ወይሄሉ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለም፡ እስእለከ፡ ወአስተበቍዓከ፡ ከመ፡ ትርድአኒ፡ ወታድኅነኒ፡ እምኵሉ፡ እኩይ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="MiraclePromises" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7311MTPromises">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ይቤ፡ አብ፡ ዘአክበረኒ፡ በምድር፡ አነ፡ አከብሮ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ገጸ፡ 
                                አርያም፡ ይመስል፡ አምሳሊሁ፡ ዘወሀበኒ፡ መባዓ፡ ወስኂነ፡ ወስንዳሌ፡ ወወይነ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Tuesday">
                    <label>Tuesday</label>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerAreyanni" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Tuesday">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ሠሉስ፡ እግዚኦ፡ አርእየኒ፡ በረከተከ፡ በዛቲ፡ ዕለት፡ ሠናይት፡ ስማዕ፡ ጸሎትየ፡ ወተወከፍ፡ ስእለትየ፡ ወሥረይ፡ ሊተ፡ ኃጢአትየ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="MiracleFather" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7314MTFather">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ አብ፡
                                ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ውስተ፡ ጽርሐ፡ አርያም፡ ወአእረፉ፡ ላእለ፡ መናብርቲሆሙ፡ ለፌ፡ ወለፌ፡ ወርእያ፡ ለዛቲ፡ በዓል፡ ዕለት፡ ዛቲሰ፡ በዓልየ፡ ወበዓለ፡ ወልድ፡ 
                                ወበዓለ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለዘአክበራ፡ ብእሲ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Wednesday">
                    <label>Wednesday</label>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerYetbarak" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Wednesday">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ረቡዕ፡ ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ አቡሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡
                                አአኵቶ፡ በኵሉ፡ ሰዓት፡ በእንተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ጸጋ፡ ዘወሀበኒ፡ ኅቡዓ፡ ወክሡተ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="MiracleReign" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7316MTReign">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ አተዉ፡ ውስተ፡ ገጸ፡ አርያም፡ ይቤ፡ አብኒ፡ ሀለወኒ፡ ጊዜ፡ ይመጽእ፡ 
                                ቃልየ፡ ወይትሌዓል፡ በ፬ ማዕዘናት፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Thursday">
                    <label>Thursday</label>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerEsebbeho" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Thursday">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ሐሙስ፡ እሴብሖ፡ ለአግዚአብሔር፡ በእንተ፡ ጸጋ፡ ዘወሀበኒ፡ ወዘአፈድፈደ፡ ላእሌየ፡ 
                                ሠናይቶ፡ ወበረከታቲሁ፡ እለ፡ አልቦን፡ ኍልቍ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="MiracleBeer" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7312MTBeer">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወሀሎ፡ ፩ ብእሲ፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡
                                ፍልስጥኤም፡ ወረሰየ፡ ምዝረ፡ በስመ፡ ሥላሴ፡  ለገቢረ፡ ተዝካሮሙ፡ ወመጽኡ፡ ብዙኃን፡ ሰይጣናት፡ ተመሲሎሙ፡
                                ከመ፡ አጽልልት፡ ወአተዉ፡ ውስተ፡ ምዝር፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Friday">
                    <label>Friday</label>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerLala">
                        <note>The text of the prayer for Friday seems to be different from the one
                            transmitted as <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Friday"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT4691Prayer#Friday</span></ref> in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet97">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 97</ref>.</note>
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ዓርብ፡ ላዕለ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ተወከልኩ፡ አምላከ፡ አብርሃም፡ ይስሐቅ፡ ወያዕቆብ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="MiracleVoice" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7315MTVoice">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡
                                ጻቃውዕ፡ ወተናገሩ፡ ጥቀ፡ ነገረ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ 
                                ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብሉ፡ </ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Saturday">
                    <label>Saturday</label>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerZafatara" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Saturday">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ ቀዳሚት፡ ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘፈጠረ፡ ሰማየ፡ ወምድረ፡ ወኵሎ፡ ዘውስቴቶሙ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="MiracleGovernor" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7313MTGovernor">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወሀሎ፡ ፩ መኰንን፡ ውስተ፡ ሀገረ፡ ፍልስጥኤም፡ ወአሐተ፡
                                ዕለተ፡ አዘዞ፡ ከመ፡ ይትጋብኡ፡  ሠራዊቱ።</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div type="textpart" xml:id="Sunday">
                    <label>Sunday</label>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerEgzieya">
                        <note>The text of the prayer for Friday seems to be different from the one
                            transmitted as <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4691Prayer#Sunday"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT4691Prayer#Sunday</span></ref> in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BAVet97">Vatican City, Biblioteca Apostolica Vaticana, Aeth. 97</ref>.</note>
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ እሁድ፡ ይትባረክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚእየ፡ ወአምላኪየ፡ እስእለከ፡ በፍቁር፡ 
                                ወልድከ፡ 
                                እግዚእነ፡ ወአምላክነ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፡ በአስማቲከ፡ ቅዱሳት፡ ከመ፡ ትስማእ፡ ጸሎትየ፡ ወአስተብቍዖትየ፡</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div type="textpart" xml:id="MiracleMonthly" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7318MTMonthly">
                        <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit">
                            <ab>ተአምራቲሆሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወአሐተ፡ ዕለተ፡ ቦኡ፡ ውስተ፡ አርያም፡ ወከሠቱ፡ አፉሆሙ፡ 
                                አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ 
                                ወይቤሉ፡ ኵሉ፡ ሕዝብ፡ ያጽምዕ፡ በበወርኁ፡ ወይከውን፡ ዕለተ፡ በዓልነ፡ ከመ፡ ዕለተ፡ ትንሣኤ።</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text></TEI>